<item>
            <title>[HADOOP-6647] balancer fails with &quot;is not authorized for protocol interface NamenodeProtocol&quot; in secure environment</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HADOOP-6647</link>
                <project id="12310240" key="HADOOP">Hadoop Common</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;user logs in as hdfs/something@something and tries to run balancer.&lt;br/&gt;
balancer is using NameNode Protocol which authorizes based on server principal key.&lt;br/&gt;
but NameNode key is hdfs/_HOST@.. now. so it fails. &lt;br/&gt;
To fix we need to compare the short names only.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
